The '''Moraabian Corporation''' was a company known to have at least meddled in genetics. [[Zyix K'zzt]] was a renowned genetic [[Scientist/Legends|scientist]] working for this corporation before he was selected by [[Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] to work for the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire's]] [[Cloning/Legends|cloning]] facilities.

